722019f-b.title: Manhattan: Park Avenue - 31st Street
722019f-b.text:
(1)
Park Ave, west side, north from but not including 31st, to, but not dncluding 33rd Streets. The view shows the Park Ave Hotel which was opened as the Women's Hotel, a semi-charitable institution in 1878 by A. T. Stewart. North of same is seen
the Vanderbilt Hotel.
December 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster, Collection.
(2)
The same, another view.
December 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster, Collection,
